glosses: A former municipality in Finland, merged with Oravainen to form Vöyri in 2011.

words.etymology_text: Vöyri + Maksamaa, originally formed as a merger of these two municipalities in 2007. After the 2011 municipal merger with Oravainen, the name Vöyri began to be used again on its own.

glosses: third-person possessive form of comitative plural of vyö

words.etymology_text: Borrowed from English worth or worth it. Doublet of verta and väärti.

glosses: from, related or pertaining to Vöyri

forms.form: Rare. Only used with substantive adjectives.

glosses: a person from or living in Vöyri
